author: Brett Hollander, WBAL
title: Brett Hollander And Rich Dubroff Talk About The Future Of Chris Davis
text:
If player does not show correctly, click here to listen . 
Rich Durbroff is the Orioles beat writer for CSN. He talks about the future of pending free agent Chris Davis with the Orioles. 
Davis won M.V.O. for the 2nd time this season and currently leads baseball in homers.
